<overview>
<ovdesc>

            <p>The records on this file are used within the MI application to assign costs as at a certain date. Whenever input to this file is validated, the data is sorted into date order, the most recent is moved to the top of the record. </p>
            <p>The costs held on this file are specified in local currency. </p>
        </ovdesc>
