<field>AMOUNT</field>
<desc>
            <p>The amount of the cost defined by this record is held here for the related DATE. </p>
            <p>Fields DATE and AMOUNT form a related multi value set. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>Standard T24 amount field.</p>
            <p>Amounts are defined in local currency.</p>
            <p>Mandatory</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>DATE</field>
<desc>
            <p>The date from which the related AMOUNT takes effect from is specified in this field. </p>
            <p>Fields DATE and AMOUNT form a related multi value set. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>Standard T24 date field.</p>
            <p>Mandatory input</p>
        </desc>
</t>
